INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a0] ON [m].[ReceiverId] = [a0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Services] AS [s] ON [m].[ServiceId] = [s].[Id]
WHERE [m].[SenderId] = @__userId_0 OR [m].[ReceiverId] = @__userId_0
ORDER BY [m].[CreatedAt] DESC
